## 9. WindowInsets (edge-to-edge)

- `enableEdgeToEdge()` en Activity ([Activity](https://developer.android.com/reference/androidx/activity/ComponentActivity#enableEdgeToEdge())).
- Modifiers oficiales: `safeDrawingPadding()`, `statusBarsPadding()`, `navigationBarsPadding()`, `imePadding()`, `displayCutoutPadding()`.
- Insets compuestos â€” solo dentro de `@Composable`:

```kotlin
@Composable
fun Modifier.horizontalSafeDrawing(): Modifier = windowInsetsPadding(
    WindowInsets.safeDrawing.only(WindowInsetsSides.Horizontal),
)
```

- No inventar insets custom si Android ya los provee.
- No apilar `safeDrawingPadding()` dentro de shells que ya aplican insets.

Referencia: [WindowInsets in Compose](https://developer.android.com/develop/ui/compose/layouts/insets).

